<div style="display:none">
    <img src="http://lehumall.b0.upaiyun.com/upload/image/admin/2016/20160928/201609281633434725.png" style="width:700px">
</div>

<!--顶部-->
<header class="header" style="border-bottom: 0px;">
    <a href="javascript:;" class="back"></a>
    <h2>幸运大转盘</h2>
    <a href="javascript:;" class="rightlink" id="share"><img src="images/coupon/share.png" style="
    height: 0.33rem;
    width: 0.33rem;
    padding: 0.275rem 0rem 0.275rem 0.275rem;
"></a>
</header>

<div class="nwrapper">
        <!--顶部-->
        <div class="dial_top">
            <div class="dial_top_box" id="nologin">
                <img src="images/carousel/lp.png">
                    请先点此<span id="login">登录</span>
            </div>
            <div class="dial_top_box" id="alreadylogin" style="display: none">
                <img src="images/carousel/lp.png">
                    剩余<span id="login">{{data.lasttimes}}</span>次机会
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!--转盘-->
        <div class="dial_main">
            <div id="lottery">
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="lottery-unit lottery-unit-0">
                            {{{lehu-lottery luckProbabilityList 0}}}
                        </td>
                        <td class="lottery-unit lottery-unit-1">
                            {{{lehu-lottery luckProbabilityList 1}}}
                        </td>
                        <td class="lottery-unit lottery-unit-2">
                            {{{lehu-lottery luckProbabilityList 2}}}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="lottery-unit lottery-unit-7">
                            {{{lehu-lottery luckProbabilityList 7}}}
                        </td>
                        <td class="lottery-bt">
                            <a href="javascript:;"></a>
                        </td>
                        <td class="lottery-unit lottery-unit-3">
                            {{{lehu-lottery luckProbabilityList 3}}}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="lottery-unit lottery-unit-6">
                            {{{lehu-lottery luckProbabilityList 6}}}
                        </td>
                        <td class="lottery-unit lottery-unit-5">
                            {{{lehu-lottery luckProbabilityList 5}}}
                        </td>
                        <td class="lottery-unit lottery-unit-4">
                            {{{lehu-lottery luckProbabilityList 4}}}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        
        <!--名单-->
        <div class="dial_msg">
            <img src="images/carousel/dial_13.png">
            <div class="dial_msg_box">
                <ul>
                {{#each zhongJiangJiLu}}
                    <li><em>{{USER_NAME}}</em><span>中了{{PRIZE}}</span><i>{{lehu-shorttime ADDTIME}}</i></li>
                {{/each}}
                </ul>
            </div>
            <img src="images/carousel/dial_16.png">
        </div>
        
        <!--说明-->
        <div class="dial_footer">
            <img src="images/carousel/dial_19.png">

            <p>
            1. 每人每天1次抽奖机会；<br/>2. 分享到朋友圈可再得一次抽奖机会；<br/>3. 抽到的优惠券与账户绑定;<br/>4. 本抽奖活动最终解释权归汇银乐虎所有，本活动与苹果公司无关。<br/>

            </p>
        </div>

        
    </div>

<div id="sharetip" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; position: fixed; top: 0px; display:none">
  <div class="mask" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);height: 100%;"></div>
  <div class="share" style="z-index:999"></div>
</div>

